<varlistentry id="options.NoIcon">
      <term><emphasis remap='I'>NoIcon</emphasis></term>
      <listitem>
<para>Disables icon from being visible when window is iconifyed. That causes window to simply disappear when the app is iconified.
Refer to the EXAMPLES below for a method to make all icons disappear.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
